      • invoke

        R invoke​(Object... args)
        Perform a var-args execution on the executable. If the Executable is an instance method, the instance should be the first argument
        Parameters:
        args - arguments to execute with
        Returns:
        return value of the invocation
        Throws:
        WrongMethodTypeException - When the number of arguments does not match the MethodType
        ClassCastException - When the type of arguments does not match the MethodType
        RuntimeException - When the underlying executable throws an exception
